Player Controls:
  - Move the player using the arrow keys OR the WASD keys
  - The player starts in slow mode, hold down "Z" while controlling the character to enter fast mode as long as the button is held down 
  - Press the space bar to shoot at enemies
  - The player has two bombs that clear enemies and bullets in a small area around the player. Press "B" to use a bomb.
  - Easy/Cheat Mode - press and hold "C" to make your character invulnerable while the key is held down.
  - Pause the game by pressing "P".
